snippet.title: Method Man Talks Relationship Goals, A Career Second Act, And His Superhero Future
snippet.description:
Clifford Smith Jr., best known as Method Man, discusses the journey that led him from hip-hop icon to Kelly Rowland's onscreen romantic partner.

Relationship Goals streams February 4 on Prime Video.
